included.summary:
Isha Patnaik is a Boston-based, Bay Area-born user experience researcher, comedian, and font enthusiast. Isha uses her cognitive science background to feed her curiosity about how people think and feel about their experiences. She is passionate about education, accessibility, and amplifying the voices of underrepresented groups. Isha also performs stand up comedy in Boston.
